raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dvc" %}
{% set version = "2.19.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 935a7373933a637a2647bc48bb973542171590a9445dcfeb38630dd2b7821aad
  patches:
    - build.patch

# The "true" build is specified in the dvc output below.
# Of the build properties here and below:
# number is propagated into the outputs below
build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [py<38]


outputs:
  - name: dvc
    build:
      entry_points:
        - dvc = dvc.main:main
      script:
        - python -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

    # Base package supports dvc, but only supports built-in remotes
    test:
      requires:
        - git
        - pip
      imports:
        - dvc
      commands:
        - pip check
        - dvc version
        - 'dvc version | grep "Supports: http, https"'

    requirements:
      host:
        - python
        - pip
      run:
        - python
        - ply >=3.9
        - colorama >=0.3.9
        - configobj >=5.0.6
        - setuptools >=48
        - nanotime >=0.5.2
        - pyasn1 >=0.4.1
        - voluptuous >=0.11.7
        - requests >=2.22.0
        - grandalf ==0.6
        - distro >=1.3.0
        - appdirs >=1.4.3
        - ruamel.yaml >=0.17.11
        - toml >=0.10.1
        - tomlkit >=0.11.1
        - funcy >=1.14
        - pathspec >=0.9.0,<0.10.0
        - shortuuid >=0.5.0
        - tqdm >=4.63.1,<5
        - packaging >=19.0
        - zc.lockfile >=1.2.1
        - flufl.lock >=5
        - networkx >=2.5,<2.8.3
        - psutil >=5.8.0
        - pydot >=1.2.4
        - importlib_resources >=5.2.2  # [py<39]
        - flatten-dict >=0.4.1,<1
        - tabulate >=0.8.7
        - pygtrie >=2.3.2
        - dpath >=2.0.2,<3
        - shtab >=1.3.4,<2
        - rich >=10.13.0
        - dictdiffer >=0.8.1
        - pyparsing ==2.4.7
        - typing_extensions >=3.7.4
        - fsspec >=2021.10.1
        - aiohttp-retry >=2.4.5
        - diskcache >=5.2.1
        - scmrepo ==0.0.25
        - dvc-render ==0.0.9
        - dvclive >=0.10.0
        - dvc-data ==0.1.15
        - dvc-http ==0.0.2
        - dvc-task ==0.1.2
        - hydra-core >=1.1.0

about:
  home: https://dvc.org/
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: DVC tracks ML models and data sets

  description: |
    Data Version Control or DVC is an open-source tool for data science
    and machine learning projects.
  doc_url: https://dvc.org/doc
  dev_url: https://github.com/iterative/dvc

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - daavoo
    - shcheklein
    - efiop
    - skshetry
    - maresb
